ActBudget Implementation Act, 2000
PrecisEnactment of an ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2000 (BONAPARTE) which adds Bonaparte to the list of Indian Bands whose Councils may make by-laws imposing a direct tax on alcoholic beverages, fuel or tobacco products.
